{"tid":1361380,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"癡撚線啲大陸人咁鐘意用對波黎開路","createTime":"2019-07-24T14:57:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T17:26:43.000Z","uid":218575,"like":25,"dislike":187,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"d695180b155c805071ca149a43bd3e9b654db937","tid":1361380,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:57:07.000Z","msg":"啱啱準備落地鐵個時因為好逼<br />\n啲人好撚似驚死落唔到咁<br />\n逼逼下feel到有樣軟綿綿嘅野係咁撞我手踭<br />\n我以為係邊個死肥佬拎個肚腩推鳩我<br />\n擰轉頭想準備屌柒佢<br />\n仆街原來係個偽韓大陸妹個波黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n癡撚線佢一啲都唔care <br />\n咁我都唔care佢撞啦 所無屌鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fb402336fa4f07777110ac59ea6664a33f10a61","tid":1361380,"uid":258236,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:57:34.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借一借位<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">728中上環遊行！！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">元朗重要，上環同樣重要</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1361287/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1361287/page/1</a><br />\n入去幫手一齊推啊！！<br />\n<br />\n728上環公海 - <a href=\"http://t.me/sw728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsw728&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0ITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=5533972d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/sw728</a><br />\nchannel - <a href=\"http://t.me/sw728update\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsw728update&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0ITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=e98a1d8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/sw728update</a><br />\n文宣 - <a href=\"https://t.me/sw728promo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsw728promo&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0ITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=fb15c5b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sw728promo</a>"},{"pid":"d698f90fe09f50ca12c93722122556f6901d9423","tid":1361380,"uid":191290,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":